---
import Layout from '../../layouts/main.astro';
---

<Layout title="Francisco J. Alpuente | Security Analyst | Blue Team">
	<main class="min-h-screen bg-slate-900 relative overflow-hidden">
		
		<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,#1e293b_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,#1e293b_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:4rem_4rem] [mask-image:radial-gradient(ellipse_60%_50%_at_50%_0%,#000_70%,transparent_100%)] opacity-20 pointer-events-none"></div>

		<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto w-full px-6 pt-24 pb-16 relative z-10">
			
			<header class="mb-20">
				<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-sky-900/30 border border-sky-700/50 text-sky-400 font-mono text-xs mb-6">
					<span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-sky-400 animate-pulse"></span>
					Open to Work: Security Analyst | Blue Team
				</div>
				<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight mb-6">
					Francisco J. Alpuente Santos
				</h1>
				<h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-slate-400 font-light mb-8 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
					After 19 years of operating critical machinery in the industrial sector, I have made the leap to <strong class="text-white font-semibold">Defensive Cybersecurity</strong>. I bring zero tolerance for failure, the rigor of ISO standards, and high-pressure incident management from the factory floor to the protection of digital infrastructures.
				</h2>
				
				<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 font-mono text-sm">
					<a href="/en/proyectos" class="bg-sky-600 hover:bg-sky-500 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded border border-sky-500 transition-colors flex items-center gap-2 shadow-lg shadow-sky-900/20">
						<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path></svg>
						View SOC Projects
					</a>
					<a href="/en/certificaciones" class="bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 text-slate-200 px-6 py-3 rounded border border-slate-600 transition-colors flex items-center gap-2">
						<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z"></path></svg>
						Hall of Fame
					</a>
					<a href="/docs/CV_Francisco_Alpuente_EN.pdf" download="CV_Francisco_Alpuente_EN.pdf" class="bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-500 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded border border-emerald-500 transition-colors flex items-center gap-2 shadow-lg shadow-emerald-900/20">
						<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4"></path></svg>
						Download CV
					</a>
				</div>
			</header>

			<section class="mb-20">
				<div class="border-l-4 border-emerald-500 pl-6 mb-10">
					<h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-3">The Advantage of Professional Maturity</h3>
					<p class="text-slate-400 max-w-2xl">
						My age and experience are not a reboot, but an added value. Cybersecurity requires mitigating risks, following procedures under pressure, and continuous improvement; exactly what I have been doing for two decades.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
					
					<div class="bg-slate-800/40 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-700/50 hover:bg-slate-800/80 transition-colors">
						<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4 text-slate-400">
							<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"></path></svg>
							<span class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">Industrial Production</span>
						</div>
						<h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">Critical Incident Management</h4>
						<p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">From managing heavy machinery where every minute of downtime costs thousands of euros, to resilience and containment under pressure during cybersecurity incidents.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-slate-800/40 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-700/50 hover:bg-slate-800/80 transition-colors">
						<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4 text-slate-400">
							<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-sky-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path></svg>
							<span class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">ISO Standards</span>
						</div>
						<h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">SLA and Playbook Compliance</h4>
						<p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">From auditing processes under strict quality standards (9001/14001), to the analytical rigor required to preserve the chain of custody during forensic triage.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-slate-800/40 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-700/50 hover:bg-slate-800/80 transition-colors">
						<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4 text-slate-400">
							<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2"></path></svg>
							<span class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">ERP Records (SAP)</span>
						</div>
						<h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">Ticketing & Meticulous Documentation</h4>
						<p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">From exact traceability of production lines, to flawless drafting of Cyber Threat Intelligence (CTI) and incident reports for executive levels.</p>
					</div>

				</div>
			</section>

		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>